<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News]]></title><link/> https://sputniknews.com/新闻<atom:link href="https://rsshub.app/sputniknews" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><description><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News - Made with love by RSSHub(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)]]></description><generator> RSSHub</generator><webmaster> i@diygod.me (DIY神)</webmaster><language> zh-cn</language><lastbuilddate> 2023 年 5 月 25 日星期四 21:16:21 GMT</lastbuilddate><ttl> 120 </ttl><item><title><![CDATA[Putin: Nagorno-Karabakh Situation Developing Towards Conflict Resolution]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110591303" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/09/17/1101115945_0:0:3720:2014_1440x900_80_0_1_94f45a964558378fe1df6a91af3b23d1.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1101115928" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230525/putin-nagorno-karabakh-situation-developing-towards-conflict-resolution-1110591303.html?share-img=1101115928"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo / Sergei Grits</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">2020 年 11 月 24 日，星期二，阿塞拜疆边境聚集在一个帐篷里，因为他们控制着纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫地区和阿塞拜疆之间新边界的一侧，靠近 Berdashen 村</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="Azerbaijanian border gather at a tent as they control their side of the new border between the region of Nagorno-Karabakh and Azerbaijan, near the village of Berdashen, Tuesday, Nov. 24, 2020 - Sputnik International, 1920, 25.05.2023" title="2020 年 11 月 24 日，星期二，阿塞拜疆边境聚集在一个帐篷里，因为他们控制着纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫地区和阿塞拜疆之间新边界的一侧，靠近 Berdashen 村" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/09/17/1101115945_71:0:3651:2014_1920x0_80_0_0_5f585a09b83b318b545703f2876aaae3.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/09/17/1101115945_71:0:3651:2014_640x0_80_0_0_4dade30521c6df1efd9d82b9edab94ec.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/09/17/1101115945_71:0:3651:2014_1280x0_80_0_0_b477cbc3a65e43004a1afa1380022cdf.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/09/17/1101115945_71:0:3651:2014_1920x0_80_0_0_5f585a09b83b318b545703f2876aaae3.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 美联社照片 / Sergei Grits </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据莫斯科（人造卫星）网报道：俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京周四在莫斯科与阿塞拜疆总统伊利哈姆·阿利耶夫和亚美尼亚总理尼科尔·帕希尼扬举行的三边会议上表示，纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫的局势正在朝着解决冲突的方向发展。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “总的来说，我认为，尽管有困难和问题，但仍然足够，但局势仍在朝着解决的方向发展。其中一个领域是交通通讯工作，”普京说。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">俄罗斯总统还表示，阿利耶夫和帕希尼扬都同意问题“可以解决”。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “在大多数情况下，他们 [问题] 不存在，”普京说。 “这些纯粹是技术问题。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110591303" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230525/putin-nagorno-karabakh-situation-developing-towards-conflict-resolution-1110591303.html?share-block=1110591306" data-title="“For the most part, they [problems] don't exist, Putin said. &quot;These are purely technical issues.&quot; "></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">普京早些时候分别与阿塞拜疆和亚美尼亚领导人举行了会谈，三边会议在大约 20 分钟后结束。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">不久之后，俄罗斯副总理阿列克谢·奥弗丘克详细说明，俄罗斯、亚美尼亚和阿塞拜疆的副总理将在下周于莫斯科举行的会议上讨论过境程序。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “具体来说，我们只会讨论过境的顺序和程序，”奥弗丘克告诉记者。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110591303" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230525/putin-nagorno-karabakh-situation-developing-towards-conflict-resolution-1110591303.html?share-block=1110591309" data-title="&quot;Specifically, we will just talk about what the order of crossing will be and what procedures will be,&quot; Overchuk told reporters."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这位官员补充说，领导人将在与副总理会谈后决定是否需要再次会面。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">最新消息是在亚美尼亚政府透露，如果其邻国保证该地区亚美尼亚人的权利和安全得到尊重，它愿意承认有争议的领土为阿塞拜疆领土。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Thu, 25 May 2023 20:59:17 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230525/putin-nagorno-karabakh-situation-developing-towards-conflict-resolution-1110591303.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230525/putin-nagorno-karabakh-situation-developing-towards-conflict-resolution-1110591303.html<category>世界</category><category>纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫</category><category>弗拉基米尔普京</category><category>伊尔哈姆阿利耶夫</category><category>尼科尔·帕希尼扬</category><category>阿塞拜疆</category><category>俄罗斯</category><category>亚美尼亚</category><category>解决冲突</category><category>三边会谈</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Peru Declares Mexican President Persona Non Grata Over Stance on Boluarte Government]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110591169" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107928/30/1079283010_0:0:3197:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_71f626dffef7d2ebbe54dd91fb3134fd.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1079283008" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230525/peru-declares-mexican-president-persona-non-grata-over-stance-on-boluarte-government-1110591169.html?share-img=1079283008"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo / Marco Ugarte</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">墨西哥总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔 (Andrés Manuel López Obrador) 于 2019 年 9 月 1 日星期日在墨西哥城国家宫发表了他第一年的国情咨文</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="Mexican President Andrés Manuel López Obrador gives his first year's state of the nation address at the National Palace in Mexico City, Sunday, Sept. 1, 2019 - Sputnik International, 1920, 25.05.2023" title="墨西哥总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔于 2019 年 9 月 1 日星期日在墨西哥城国家宫发表了他第一年的国情咨文" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107928/30/1079283010_0:126:3197:1924_1920x0_80_0_0_e3cdb607a2598f0006768de6a3ea5cf7.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107928/30/1079283010_0:126:3197:1924_640x0_80_0_0_8627f921516870149fdf13a9f3a52179.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107928/30/1079283010_0:126:3197:1924_1280x0_80_0_0_3ea0ef08acc2a804c87081442644981b.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107928/30/1079283010_0:126:3197:1924_1920x0_80_0_0_e3cdb607a2598f0006768de6a3ea5cf7.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 美联社照片 / Marco Ugarte </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据墨西哥城（人造卫星）网报道：秘鲁国会周四宣布墨西哥总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔不受欢迎。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “国会全体会议以 65 票赞成通过了第 6513 号议案，提议宣布墨西哥总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔为不受欢迎的人，”秘鲁国会在推特上表示。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">奥夫拉多尔表示，秘鲁总统迪娜博卢阿尔特的政府是非法的，称她为“篡位者”，因为她参与了许多人认为推翻她的前任佩德罗卡斯蒂略的阴谋。 2月24日，博卢阿尔特谴责墨西哥总统对秘鲁“内政”的“不可接受”干涉。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">秘鲁议会于 12 月 7 日弹劾了卡斯蒂略，时任总理的博卢阿尔特在弹劾投票后两小时内宣誓就任该国新总统。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">卡斯蒂略曾试图在投票前解散议会，但在弹劾程序后被捕，秘鲁检察官办公室以涉嫌政变未遂和危害国家罪对他提起刑事诉讼。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 12 月中旬，卡斯蒂略被判处 18 个月的审前拘留。据当地媒体报道，这些事件导致秘鲁各地发生大规模示威游行，抗议活动导致至少 60 人死亡。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">示威者谴责弹劾后的博卢阿尔特政府，并呼吁立即举行总统选举并解散该国议会。由于抗议活动中有公民死亡，秘鲁检察官办公室对博卢阿尔特和现任总理阿尔贝托·奥塔罗拉发起种族灭绝调查。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Thu, 25 May 2023 20:49:48 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230525/peru-declares-mexican-president-persona-non-grata-over-stance-on-boluarte-government-1110591169.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230525/peru-declares-mexican-president-persona-non-grata-over-stance-on-boluarte-government-1110591169.html<category>美洲</category><category>安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔</category><category>佩德罗卡斯蒂略</category><category>迪娜博卢亚特</category><category>秘鲁</category><category>墨西哥</category><category>秘鲁国会</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[What is Turkish Presidential System and How Does It Work?]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110589063" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/104413/92/1044139289_0:0:3500:2333_1440x900_80_0_1_6f5e92742a75d524f29b4e8416187994.jpg?source-sid=afp" data-photoview-image-id="1044139288" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230525/what-is-turkish-presidential-system-and-how-does-it-work-1110589063.html?share-img=1044139288"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© <a href="https://ria.ru/docs/about/copyright_afp.html" title="法新社 2023">AFP 2023</a> / ADEM ALTAN /</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">土耳其国旗。 （文件）</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="afp" alt="Turkish flag. (File) - Sputnik International, 1920, 25.05.2023" title="土耳其国旗。 （文件）" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/104413/92/1044139289_0:182:3500:2151_1920x0_80_0_0_bbd574de7487df7fc42542612a0da5ae.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/104413/92/1044139289_0:182:3500:2151_640x0_80_0_0_e50214387ee3f919ff3a6c2b678ee010.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/104413/92/1044139289_0:182:3500:2151_1280x0_80_0_0_fd27c61eeefa61896a8fc914df587ae8.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/104413/92/1044139289_0:182:3500:2151_1920x0_80_0_0_bbd574de7487df7fc42542612a0da5ae.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © <a href="https://ria.ru/docs/about/copyright_afp.html" title="法新社 2023">AFP 2023</a> / ADEM ALTAN / </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">安德烈·德加林</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_dergalin_andrei/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:a.dergalin@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">过去是议会制共和国，不到十年前，Turkiye 转变为总统制，在这种制度下，以前由目前已废除的总理和总统职位划分的行政权现在完全属于后者。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">由于该国正在进行的<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230524/turkish-fm-expects-erdogan-to-gain-over-56-in-election-runoff-1110553103.html" target="_blank">总统选举</a>，Turkiye 在过去几周一直成为头条新闻。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">由于没有候选人能够在 5 月 14 日的第一轮投票中获胜，决胜期定于 5 月 28 日举行。第二轮投票将由土耳其选民在现任总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安和反对派之间做出选择领导人凯末尔·基利达罗格鲁。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">那么，一位<strong>土耳其总统</strong>实际拥有多少权力，又该如何担任这一职位呢？</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="h2"><h2 class="article__h2">土耳其是民主国家吗？</h2></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">直到最近，土耳其还是一个议会制共和国，行政权由作为国家元首的总统和作为政府首脑的总理划分。虽然该国的议会，即大国民议会，是通过普选产生的，但总统的选举是议会的职责。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">然而，在2007年宪法公投之后，选举总统领导人的权力从议会转移，通过<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230524/turkish-fm-expects-erdogan-to-gain-over-56-in-election-runoff-1110553103.html" target="_blank">普选的方式直接交给土耳其公众。</a></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">十年后，2017 年举行的另一次宪法公投导致总理职位被废除，政府首脑的角色被移交给总统。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">后一项改革有效地导致了 Turkiye 转向<strong>总统制</strong>。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="h3"><h3 class="article__h2">谁能当选土耳其总统？</h3></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">根据土耳其宪法的原则，总统候选人必须年满<strong>40 岁</strong>且至少完成<strong>高等教育</strong>。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="h3"><h3 class="article__h2">土耳其总统是如何选出的？</h3></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">目前，土耳其的总统选举是通过<strong>普选</strong>进行的，任何<strong>年满 18 岁的</strong>土耳其公民都可以投票。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">如果一名候选人未能获得绝对多数选票，将举行第二轮投票，选民必须在第一轮投票中获得最多选票的两名候选人之间做出选择。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="h3"><h3 class="article__h2">土耳其总统有什么权力？</h3></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">土耳其共和国总统本质上是土耳其的国家元首，国家的<strong>行政权力</strong>归于他。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">总统可以任命部长和高级公共行政人员，批准国际条约，就行政权力事项发布法令，甚至将法律发回议会重新审议等职责。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">他们作为土耳其武装部队总司令的地位也使总统能够就土耳其军事力量的使用做出决定。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="h3"><h3 class="article__h2">土耳其总统可以统治多长时间？什么是任期限制？</h3></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">根据土耳其法律，总统任期为<strong>五年</strong>，一人最多可连任<strong>两届</strong>。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Thu, 25 May 2023 19:57:10 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230525/what-is-turkish-presidential-system-and-how-does-it-work-1110589063.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230525/what-is-turkish-presidential-system-and-how-does-it-work-1110589063.html<category>世界</category><category>突厥耶</category><category>总统职位</category><category>总统制</category><category>总统选举</category></item></channel></rss>